\lim_{(x,y)\to (0,0)} \frac{\left | x \right |^{\frac{3}{2}}y^{2}}{x^{4} + y^{2}} \rightarrow 0\;?
y \neq 0
 0 \le \frac{{|x|^{3/2} y^2 }}{{x^4  + y^2 }} = \frac{{|x|^{3/2} }}{{x^4 /y^2  + 1}} \le \frac{{|x|^{3/2} }}{1} = |x|^{3/2}  \to 0. 
0 \le \frac{{y^2 }}{{x^4  + y^2 }} \le 1
(x,y) \neq (0,0)
\frac{{|x|^{3/2} y^2 }}{{x^4  + y^2 }} \to 0
x \to 0
y
x=r\cos \theta
y=r\sin\theta
\lim_{(x,y)\rightarrow (0,0)}\frac{|x|^\frac{3}{2}y^2}{x^4+y^2}= 0.
\lim_{(x,y)\rightarrow(0,0)}\frac{|x|^{\frac{3}{2}}y^{2}}{x^{4}+y^{2}}=\lim_{r\rightarrow0}\frac{r^{\frac{3}{2}}|\cos\theta|^{\frac{3}{2}}r^{2}\sin^{2}\theta}{r^{2}\left(r^{2}\cos^{4}\theta+\sin^{2}\theta\right)}=\lim_{r\rightarrow0}r^{\frac{3}{2}}\frac{|\cos\theta|^{\frac{3}{2}}}{\left(r^{2}\cos^{4}\theta/\sin^{2}\theta+1\right)}.
0\leq \frac{|\cos\theta|^{\frac{3}{2}}}{\left(r^{2}\cos^{4}\theta/\sin^{2}\theta+1\right)}\leq |\cos\theta|^\frac{3}{2}\leq 1
\lim_{r\rightarrow 0}r^\frac{3}{2}=0
0
